content.raw:
Can you re-post the link you’re following?

Edit: is it [this one](#!/osrf/subt/wiki/tutorials/SystemSetupInstall)?

You may have an older version of protobuf installed on your native OS that’s causing interference.  If you can’t compile after 

```
sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get upgrade -y
catkin_make clean && catkin_make install
```

then I believe you have some funky packages installed on your native OS that are causing issues.
